                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><strong>Education:</strong> B. of Science, Computer Science, Minor in Entrepreneurship, Baylor University</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><strong>Favorite Genres of Music:</strong> Yes</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><strong>Spotify or Apple Music:</strong> Apple Music</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p><strong>Favorite Web Technologies:</strong> Svelte, Astro, PHP</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!--Links-->
        <div>
            <p>Interesting Links About Me Here</p>
        </div>
    </div>






</MySiteLayout>